    C -->|Auto-redirect after 3s| G["www.yourbrand.com<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>Main Website<br/>(Final Destination)"]

    style A fill:#010101,stroke:#fe2c55,color:#fff
    style B fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#00d4ff,color:#fff
    style C fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#ffa500,color:#fff
    style D fill:#0088cc,stroke:#0088cc,color:#fff
    style E fill:#e1306c,stroke:#e1306c,color:#fff
    style F fill:#333,stroke:#888,color:#fff
    style G fill:#0d5f1c,stroke:#00ff41,color:#fff
```

### Architecture Properties Summary

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| **Maximum redirect depth** | 2 (bio → link page → soft redirect → website) |
| **Unique domains in chain** | 2 (`links.yourbrand.com` + `www.yourbrand.com`, same parent domain) |
| **Third-party dependencies** | Zero |
| **Cloaking risk** | Zero (identical content for all clients) |
| **Telegram link exposure** | Single point (link-in-bio page only) |
| **Analytics method** | First-party, same-origin, beacon-based |
| **Estimated user drop-off** | 15-25% (industry standard for 1-hop funnel) |
| **Long-term stability** | High (you control every component) |
| **Detection risk classification** | 🟢 Low |

> [!TIP]
> **Implementation priority order:**
> 1. Register and age your domain (if new) — start immediately
> 2. Deploy `links.yourbrand.com` with the link-in-bio page
> 3. Add the soft redirect page for website navigation
> 4. Set up first-party analytics
> 5. Polish branding and UX
> 6. Set the link in your TikTok bio
